    <info publication="20080120120000">
        <license name="Apache License, Version 2.0" url="http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0"/>
        <description homepage="http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-io/">
        <p>Commons IO is a library of utilities to assist with developing IO functionality.</p>
        
        There are four main areas included:
        <ul>
            <li>Utility classes - with static methods to perform common tasks</li>
            <li>Filters - various implementations of file filters</li>
            <li>Comparators - various implementations of java.util.Comparator for files</li>
            <li>Streams - useful stream, reader and writer implementations</li>
        </ul>
        </description>
    </info>

    <publications>
